Gloria Wood https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gloria_Wood 0 Gloria Wood (September 8, 1923 – March 4, 1995) was an American singer and voice actress. Her rare voice was in the four-octave range. She was able to imitate other voices. Gloria_Wood ( September_8_,_1923 – March_4_,_1995 ) was an_American_singer_and_voice_actress . Her_rare_voice was in the_four-octave_range . She was able to_imitate other_voices .
